<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Each Member State shall, subject to Article 4, take all appropriate measures to ensure that civil liability in respect of the use of vehicles normally based in its territory is covered by insurance. </inglise>
<eesti> Iga liikmesriik v&otilde;tab artiklit 4 arvestades k&otilde;ik vajalikud meetmed tagamaks, et nende s&otilde;idukite kasutamisel, mille p&otilde;hiasukoht on tema territooriumil, on tsiviilvastutus kaetud kindlustusega. </eesti>
<inglise> The extent of the liability covered and the terms and conditions of the cover shall be determined on the basis of these measures. </inglise>
