<inglise> Upon having ascertained, in close cooperation with the Member States, that the obligations referred to in the preceding paragraph have been assumed, the Commission shall fix the date from which and the types of vehicles for which Member States shall no longer require production of the documents referred to in paragraph 1. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui tihedas kost&ouml;&ouml;s liikmesriikidega on kindlaks tehtud, et eelmises l&otilde;ikes osutatud kohustused on v&otilde;etud, m&auml;&auml;rab komisjon kindlaks, millisest kuup&auml;evast alates ja mis liiki s&otilde;idukite puhul ei n&otilde;ua liikmesriigid enam l&otilde;ikes 1 osutatud dokumentide esitamist. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 8 </inglise>
